Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:03:00.51,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(1098,599)}暴风雨之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不允许搜索里亚赞少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索下级士官有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 还是要优先寻找多尔杰夫阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都还不知道坠落到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被击落的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔基姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体的修理和补给一结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就马上和搜索队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对死人献媚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不能允许对青叶君进行搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面可是暴风雨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要尽快找到青叶同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上天气恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是脱离了战线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人可能也还在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,valiancer和Cygnus也并非毫无损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最优先考虑成员们的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的判断有错吗 李君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…联结机要两台齐备才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是权衡一切之后的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰将继续保持警戒态势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雨过后 开始移动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,valiancer队为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以随时可以出击的状态待机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还像个孩子一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是不让他干 就越是想要干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是强硬撬开了逐渐沉没的座舱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你拉出来带到了这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要俘虏你 证明我的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样怎么说都动不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包好像也被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要调查一下你的valiancer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是联结机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也拿到了救生包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟 能使用无线电的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等天晴了再详细调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一点感谢之情都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想说终于见到你了 这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虏不要多说废话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个放下啊 话说那个本来就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被夺走了救生包 你是个不称职的军人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在是军人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会让这种人搭乘新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为被你带来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校突然被valiancer袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你救了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 说「迪奥在等你」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我送到这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,70年后的这个世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然让这种男人当新型机的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联合看来相当缺人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:06:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 你为什么会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 你是我的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫弓原雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被valiancer袭击的时候 你救了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同学？救你？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净说些莫名其妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事我要先告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你说的雏跟我有多么相像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是配属于佐基利亚军第101独立侦查旅团的少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维克多·里亚赞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我10岁就读于第11幼年士官学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业后 经利佩茨克基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配属于第501机动中队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能和你有过接触
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑啊 那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了见到雏才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就交由我军调查部来调查你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过暴风圈了 现在可以飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不算回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能失去LUXON
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长有话托我转告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三小时为限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了三小时就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是连迪奥也行踪不明就麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有句话叫适得其反啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有另外一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾维拉小姐托我转告的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定 联结机器可以帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没找到多尔杰夫阁下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在进行搜索 但是还没有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被击落在一望无际的大海中的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没那种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 比森
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 不是说FORTUNA啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是坠落而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心说话 塔基姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比森和我们不同 从小就认识雏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和雏虽然是同一个班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却基本没怎么说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她救我的时候差不多是第一次说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我连她是什么样的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本想见到她之后 问她很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要救我之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎样才能回到原本的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我以为终于见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却告诉我是另外一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 她去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然已经不能回到原本的时代了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把火灭了 什么都看不到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我 是被风吹灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得包里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全被堵住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说 幸好火灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有空气循环
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚会缺氧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在挖沙土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想和敌人白白死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起一个人干 还是两个人更快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把这个切断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我什么都不会做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是稍微有一点奇怪的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 我不会那么做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 要挖多少才能出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挖来挖去 马上就从上面掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 休息结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看原篮球部的体力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙…沙土从上面掉到了下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定顶点附近 沙土更薄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是亲卫师团长的机体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟预想一样的结果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比森
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后 我们部队将采取独自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师团长阁下的战死已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务应该已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没找到？差不多要到三小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说被海流冲走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就要重新计算搜索范围了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是还活着 就赶快发出求救信号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸困难了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 振作一点 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说缺氧了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会让你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样…死在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上带你上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的一无所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洞穴也在海中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在这里等暴风雨过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶…青…听到…回话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奥联络了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现青叶同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 联结系统真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然可以通过数倍扩大联结可能领域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定同伴机的位置 远距离启动它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么原理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 当然是开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这个模式消耗能量非常厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说三小时 却没能回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 我会严重警告他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也找到了 可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边怎么样了 敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌…敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 快点报告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然电波状态…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐基利亚的通信周波数是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要取得联络啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要告诉佐基利亚 雏在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊 就算过了70年 朝阳也不会改变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要让我联系佐基利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那样的话 雏就会成为我们的俘虏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个不称职的军人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奥好像来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边也有人来接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就赶快藏起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是雏的发夹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是飞到这边的时候 一起带着的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我不是那个雏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想让你拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 你可以走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫渡濑青叶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 哟 辛苦你们来接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 切断通信是想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊 电波状态突然变糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种谎话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算啦 青叶君平安归来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会再问你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这话迪奥可以说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快回收
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等啊 我还没坐上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡濑…青叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:40.16,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(631,474)}下回「联结系统」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 BUDDY COMPLEX 联结系统
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:23.23,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,心で呼ぶ　惹かれあう彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:23.23,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,心的呼应 响应的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:31.88,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,痛みの理由(わけ)も忘れて　今だけどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:31.88,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,痛的理由 请暂且忘记 我在此深深祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:41.08,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを知っている　キミを探しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:41.08,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,我深知你 我在一直寻找着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:49.80,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,引き止められない光の残像に　そっとくちづけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:49.80,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻吻向那已飘渺的光的残像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:58.81,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,躊躇いが僅かな　希望への糸口なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:58.81,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,你那稍稍的犹豫不决 成为了那连接希望的蛛丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:07.52,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,彷徨った数だけ　優しい朝へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:07.52,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,你那微微的彷徨 拉近了与那温柔黎明的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:16.56,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,あの空に還る未来で　救いたい　守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:16.56,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,想去拯救 想去保护 那早已归还于天空的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:23.44,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,その夢に届く未来で　待っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:23.44,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,请留步 那已经早已传达过梦想的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:32.86,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと出会える愛に　手を伸ばして欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:32.86,EDZ,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能与我一起去抓住 那注定相遇的爱
